<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 You are close to me
 But I long to hear Your heart
 Lord, I know Your ways
 And I can feel Your touch

[V2]
 Your presence is all I need
 I close my eyes and You draw near
 Lord...

[V3]
 Lord, Your love is like desert rain
 Lord, Your love is like a sea of stars by day
 Lord, Your love is like a fire
 Purifying and consuming me
 Your love changes me

[V4]
 Your love sets me free
 Your love changes me</lyrics>
<title>Your Love</title>
<author>Evan Schoombie</author>
<hymn_number>328</hymn_number>
</song>